data.description: Move right into this wonderful 3 bedroom / 2 full bathroom ranch located in Arlington Heights!! This home has the desirable split bedroom floor-plan, with a master bedroom that offers a vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet and full bathroom. On the opposite side of the home there are 2 more spacious bedrooms and additional full bathroom. Walking in through the foyer, you will love the cathedral ceiling that flows from front to back into the great room that features a gas fireplace, skylights and patio door leading to a screened back porch with a cathedral ceiling. The eat-in kitchen has stainless steel appliances, a 3/4th wall with opening into the great room and ample cabinet space. Off the kitchen is a laundry/mechanical room with access to the oversized 2 car garage. Recent updates include new Coretec LVP in the foyer, kitchen, bathrooms, new roof with replacement skylights and new overhead garage door on order. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, trails, 469 and the Jackson R. Lehman family YMCA, this is a must see!
